下不同聲音或政治打壓，又強調決定是合憲、合法、合理，理所當然，完全符合基本法，任何質疑決定無法律根據的批評是謬誤言論。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗表示，有人慣性打着民主、人權、自由的旗號，甚至說出民主倒退，<span class=\"gold\">一國兩制終結和一國一制開始等歪理，是顛倒是非黑白，肆意抹黑和惡意攻擊國家，藉機惡意破壞和挑撥港人對國家的感情</span>，企圖昭然若揭，但不會得逞，強調香港事務是中國內政，外國政府不應干涉。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2366316&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BEbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=ec12b513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366316</a>"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T01:05:59.000Z","msg":"中港融合都唔提得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:05:03.000Z","msg":"從今開始應稱香港警察為中国香港警察<br />\n邊個唔加就係想搞港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f39a67e93aa0986ef4cd2f054e737236ec33166","tid":2286300,"uid":39492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:12:32.000Z","msg":"篤灰熱線用得著啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4edf5523b85afe576b93b5e6fc3372a880395347","tid":2286300,"uid":379666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:12:52.000Z","msg":"上面好多中國人要求一國一制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外國就拉唔到姐 係中國拉到啦掛"},{"pid":"778d45d9e24ae453bf1058bee9168b58852b7d8e","tid":2286300,"uid":283222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:13:11.000Z","msg":"嘩！大O樂！好多建制派人講過要一國一制，秋後算帳？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55582f39f9f67e60257f32d5c93fe05deef8d6e9","tid":2286300,"uid":88725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:14:33.000Z","msg":"講呢d 你老細習大大黑曬面<img src=\"/assets/faces